<body>
    <h1>Get Loyalty Programs</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"0a25a911df24"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"e88d842d1ef2"><strong>Category:</strong> Property Configurat=
ion</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"aee31de85c9d" id=3D"GetLoyaltyPrograms-Overview">Overview</=
h2>
<p local-id=3D"d16fa1bf0a70">The <strong>Get Loyalty Programs</strong> acti=
on retrieves a list of all loyalty programs configured at your property. It=
 requires no input parameters =E2=80=94 when triggered, it automatically fe=
tches every active loyalty program associated with the property and returns=
 them as a list of name=E2=80=93value pairs.</p>
<p local-id=3D"995f501acf6c">This component is commonly used as a data sour=
ce to populate dropdown selectors in other components, or to feed loyalty p=
rogram information into subsequent steps of a workflow. For example, you co=
uld use it to let a user select a loyalty program when building a guest enr=
ollment flow, or to iterate over all programs and perform an action for eac=
h one.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c6ade85d-91cd-464b-b3c8-e876ae98b9ca">
<h2 local-id=3D"a2ffdb46cafe" id=3D"GetLoyaltyPrograms-InputFields">Input F=
ields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8bbf897e90d8">This component has <strong>no input fields</st=
rong>. It does not require any configuration or parameters to run. When it =
receives a signal on its input port, it automatically retrieves all loyalty=
 programs for the authenticated property.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"f1159b21-8bf1-494b-b2e5-6a4aa11f09e7">
<h2 local-id=3D"5debd9658b34" id=3D"GetLoyaltyPrograms-OutputFields">Output=
 Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"64dd7192eebf">When the loyalty programs are successfully ret=
rieved, the following values are available on the <strong>out</strong> outp=
ut port for use in subsequent workflow steps:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"443f382f-a7fc-4a7f-aaa0-734=
522c84c9d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d6e26f19-1bae-4d6d-89fe-b8226c37f4a0">
<th data-local-id=3D"0927ac86-50d9-41ac-acff-a1aff43497e3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2c50860b7711">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"526941b6-7d0e-4dd6-893d-f530fc094953" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"442e3aad7615">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d2d5d1bd-fb60-494a-ba72-ee0ff86010f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b42fc397e741">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e04e3eda-4b48-40cf-8e65-8c06811763c8">
<td data-local-id=3D"a7c2b75a-9ee9-400d-8e75-4b4203055b7c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2d403a4e4d9a"><strong>Items</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c3572911-dbae-4466-a01a-ee24e8b16a5b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2607a7e5505b">Array of objects</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"926f5731-794e-4a0f-8c66-7796daa40986" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a2de246c187d">A list of loyalty programs. Each item in the a=
rray contains:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1b53f86d-6453-4ddd-8f53-ecd5937d9081">
<li local-id=3D"9bdd448d-27c0-44aa-9162-28b5cd926364">
<p local-id=3D"4ac88fa456d7"><strong>Value</strong> (Text) =E2=80=94 The un=
ique identifier (GUID) of the loyalty program. Use this value when passing =
a loyalty program reference to other components.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f8f0526-4184-463c-b731-2184b2c2443d">
<p local-id=3D"8e6f21c2d53a"><strong>Label</strong> (Text) =E2=80=94 The di=
splay name of the loyalty program as configured in Mews. If a program has n=
o name set, the label defaults to <code>Unknown</code>.</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"4e9666c774c9"><strong>Note:</strong> If no loyalty programs =
are configured at the property, the component returns an empty list. When u=
sed as a dropdown data source in other components, an empty list displays a=
s <strong>"No results"</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"859f4030-7977-4f8d-b035-ce5ffdb1feed">
<h2 local-id=3D"29144c38a235" id=3D"GetLoyaltyPrograms-HowItWorks">How It W=
orks</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e3ca501f-ffd2-4d81-929e-cca9d5bbf45d">
<li local-id=3D"bdc9acc6-dff1-4723-b4d2-b2bd9312c517">
<p local-id=3D"aba3fc2a6f92">The component receives a signal from the previ=
ous step in the workflow (or is triggered manually).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d980a6af-78cc-47cd-bd09-b5f4df624698">
<p local-id=3D"571a267499f2">It sends a request to the Mews backend to retr=
ieve all active loyalty programs associated with the authenticated property=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df33b2b9-b160-4bbd-bc4a-bcafd60843b2">
<p local-id=3D"26ea313a8556">The backend identifies the property's chain an=
d returns every active loyalty program that belongs to that chain.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca8db2c3-06d9-4039-b194-d9eeee7c2fdc">
<p local-id=3D"2194ce01c008">The list of programs is returned on the <stron=
g>out</strong> output port as an array of name=E2=80=93value pairs, where e=
ach entry contains the program's unique identifier and display name.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"93b6af02-23fc-41dc-9116-7073807fd8f7">
<p local-id=3D"281bf6f2c97b">If the request fails (e.g., due to a connectiv=
ity issue), the component returns an error.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"a4a13b7d-c3f6-4967-906a-1760cb321530">
<h2 local-id=3D"af9cc052bf30" id=3D"GetLoyaltyPrograms-ExampleUseCases">Exa=
mple Use Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"5e9f7708-89c4-44ab-962a-d332cccd5209">
<li local-id=3D"bff67616-c540-4500-8801-7631532603b1">
<p local-id=3D"36b0642cd9b4"><strong>Populate a loyalty program selector</s=
trong> =E2=80=94 Use this component as a dynamic data source to populate a =
dropdown field in another component, allowing users to select a specific lo=
yalty program when configuring a workflow.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c962fd9-1f27-4d58-88df-09e947a3e854">
<p local-id=3D"a61cdc85e137"><strong>Guest enrollment workflow</strong> =E2=
=80=94 Retrieve the list of available loyalty programs and, based on guest =
profile data, automatically enroll the guest in a matching program.</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"3bc1e74b-6632-4d7d-a894-6326c24d1253">
<p local-id=3D"7ba6dd1b0537"><strong>Loyalty program audit</strong> =E2=80=
=94 Periodically fetch all loyalty programs and compare against an expected=
 list to verify that all programs are correctly configured at the property.=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"de380fee-47ab-4579-80d0-b3aab4896c74">
<h2 local-id=3D"5574e85f78b2" id=3D"GetLoyaltyPrograms-ErrorHandling">Error=
 Handling</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"1f36f855-4459-4930-b0e1-e73=
7b2145d88" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2d42413f-6ae7-4fae-b24f-40e3bea7b3ef">
<th data-local-id=3D"6003baf0-16f0-4b1e-9f59-68d9a8f64d40" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1a2461687e53">Error</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"14e1f6a0-94fc-4771-bfeb-8543c08b6836" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"8a598df9350f">Cause</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c2d43d08-1a3f-4da7-b403-e47cb1231c82">
<td data-local-id=3D"03743697-78f0-41ed-ab2b-5692a9f7c7bf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cafdd08ae3d9"><code>Request failed</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f63e9995-954d-4c0e-9ee4-9726dc5bd7b7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5492ebfeaf87">The request to retrieve loyalty programs from =
Mews failed. This may indicate a temporary service issue or an authenticati=
on problem.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
